*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form addit
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> P_OP1
*&      --> P_OP2
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM addit  USING    p_p_op1
                     p_p_op2.

  v_resultado =  p_p_op1 +  p_p_op1.

ENDFORM.



*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form sub
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> P_OP1
*&      --> P_OP2
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM sub  USING    p_p_op1
                   p_p_op2.

 v_resultado = p_p_op1 - p_p_op2.

ENDFORM.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form mult
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> P_OP1
*&      --> P_OP2
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM mult  USING    p_p_op1
                    p_p_op2.

v_resultado = p_p_op1 *  p_p_op2.

ENDFORM.



